@*REGISTER TO VOTE BY MAIL SECTION*@
<div class="allRegContainer">
    <div id="Register" class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title">Vote By Mail</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
               Dont' want to stand in line on election day? Want to vote from the comfort of your own home? Well you can! All you have to do is send in a form either by mail or online to request your ballot.
                <br /><br />
                Request your ballot below.
                <p id="b1"><a target="_blank" href="http://boe.cuyahogacounty.us/en-US/VoteByMail.aspx" class="btn btn-primary" role="button">Online</a><a target="_blank" href="http://boe.cuyahogacounty.us/pdf_boe/en-US/Applications/absenteeApplication2012e.pdf" class="btn btn-default" role="button">By Mail</a></p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    @*TRACK BALLOT SECTION*@

    <div id="CheckReg" class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title">Track Your Ballot</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                Want to make sure your vote by mail ballot made it to be counted? Check the status of your absentee ballot below.
                <p id="b2"><a target="_blank" href="http://boe.cuyahogacounty.us/en-US/track-my-ballot.aspx" class="btn btn-primary" role="button">Track Ballot</a></p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    @*FIND POLLING LOCATION SECTION*@
    <div id="UpdateName" class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title">Find Your Polling Location</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                So, it's Election Day and you're ready to vote, but you don't know your polling location? No problem. We've got you. Find your polling location below.
                <p id="b3"><a target="_blank" href="http://boe.cuyahogacounty.us/en-US/My-Polling-Location.aspx" class="btn btn-primary" role="button">Find Your Poll</a></p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
